projects.description:
Any registered user in the app can send notification messages uptil a certain specified range in case of emergency situation(unicast and multicast facility added on).
Also the user can add his own marker in the Google map (on -touch) on the screen and post/edit responses about a certain place and can send to one person or many person (private and public tagging features).
When another new user arrives, that person can see the previous posts about any particular place(wherever marker was added).
Successfully deployed the app .Now end users can avail the advantage of this app.

Link: https://bhowmiktiasha.github.io(not mobile responsive though)
